        Let me know if you have a cool dataset you think I should make a map of. If you're feeling adventurous, you can make one of your own by starting with
        = succeed "." do
          %a{:href => "http://derekeder.com/searchable_map_template/"} this
      .grid-item
        %a{:href => "/maps/chicago-clinics/"} 
          %img.img-polaroid{:src => "/images/icons/clinic.png", :title => "Health Clinics in Chicago"}/
          %h4
            Health Clinics in Chicago
        %p Find Neighborhood, Mental Health and Women, Infants & Children (WIC) clinics in Chicago.
        
      .grid-item
        %a{:href => "/maps/chicago-bike-crash-reports/"} 
          %img.img-polaroid{:src => "/images/icons/cyclingsport.png", :title => "Chicago Bike Crash Reports"}/
          %h4
            Chicago Bike Crash Reports
        %p Searchable map of nearly 5,000 reported bicycle crashes in the City of Chicago from 2007-2009 as reported to the Illinois Department of Transportation. Recently added some more advanced filters.
        
      .grid-item
        %a{:href => "/maps/cook-county-hospitals/"} 
          %img.img-polaroid{:src => "/images/icons/doctor.png", :title => "Cook County Hospitals"}/
          %h4
            Cook County Hospitals
        %p All hospitals in Cook County compared to ward and neighborhood.
        
      .grid-item
        %a{:href => "/maps/2011-IL-senate-redistricting-plan/"} 
          %img.img-polaroid{:src => "/images/icons/congress.png", :title => "2011 IL Senate Redistricting Plan"}/
          %h4
            2011 IL Senate Redistricting Plan
        %p
          View the IL senate's redistricting plan released on May 19th, 2011 to see what district you will fall in
          and compare it to the existing 2001 boundaries.
        
      .grid-item
        %a{:href => "/maps/chicago-tif/"} 
          %img.img-polaroid{:src => "/images/icons/bank.png", :title => "Chicago TIF Projects"}/
          %h4
            Chicago TIF Projects
        %p
          I teamed up with a group of journalism students from Columbia College to present a searchable map of Tax Increment Financing (TIF) Projects in Chicago. Also includes a heat map of amounts allocated per ward.
          %br/
          %strong Press:
          %a{:href => "http://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/27/us/27cnctif.html"} New York Times
          |
          %a{:href => "http://www.chicagonewscoop.org/corporate-giants-received-tif-money-records-show/comment-page-1/"} Chicago News Cooperative
          |
          %a{:href => "http://www.chicagotalks.org/2011/02/26/tif-subsidies-given-to-chicago-companies-nonprofits-bypass-city-neighborhoods-in-need-of-jobs/"} ChicagoTalks
